  m_text: "Save Your Friend\n\nIf you see a circle on the arms, legs, and head -
    wait until the outer ring turns green to attack. \n\ntiming is everythiing/ If
    you miss the time, the doll loses health and if you dont click at all, YOU lose
    health\n\nif the big circle appears on the chest, you need to perform CPR to
    keep your doll alive in order to save your friend\n\nto save your freind, u must
    sapm awzxd, press all the dolls limbs to squeeze her amout befroe the next attack
    begins\n"
